%h1.logo Beatr

%p Realtime heartbeats for anything.

.instructions
  %h3 How do I get started?
  %section
    %h4 Download the Beatr gem:
    %p
      %code.bash
        $ gem install beatr

  %section
    %h4 Send your Beats:
    %p
      %code.ruby
        Beatr.beat 'my-startup-signups'

  %section
    %h4 Watch the Beats live at your URL:
    %p
      %code.http
        http://beatr.io/my-startup-signups

